 main components of the halo and the ratio of accreted\ncomponents do not show clear relation to Galactic radius.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Jan 2021 06:15:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Jan 2021 10:44:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-23"}
